node.text:
It’s Sunday and we’re not ready to stop the fun!
Lets keep it going with our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm, our amazing rooftop for drinks, we have our t dance at 6pm AND our evening shows from 7-1130pm!! 

We have a fun filled day and we hope you’re ready! 🙌🏽💃🏽💥🔥

The gorgeous @marinavgregory giving us looks and enjoying her time at PALACE and having our delicious salmon plate 🤤

node.text:
Let’s keep the energy going on this weekend!! Rain or shine we’re celebrating with you! 
Let’s have you at our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm and our evening shows from 7-1130pm! Join us and let’s have fun and a refreshing drink at PALACE 

Our talented @tloivy performing @janetjackson #feedback

May be an image of 1 person, standing, parrot and text.

node.text:
It’s Friday and we’re ready for the weekend!! Join us as we kick off the weekend with our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm- 
We give you great shows, music and our amazing staff members like @the_famous_frankk will bring you delicious food, drinks and hookahs! Let’s get it started!

It’s Friday and we’re ready to get the weekend started!! 
Let’s celebrate together, starting with our brunch shows at 11am and 2pm, let’s grab a delicious drink on our rooftop and then continue the fun with our evening shows from 7-1130pm 🙌🏽💥💃🏽💃🏽

One of our dancing queens @tiara_love_dupree performing @kelis
